stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pipeline : POST /api/challenges/launch

    state "Launch Pipeline (SSE stream)" as Pipeline {
        Generating : Generating\nOpenRouter + Zod + policy
        Deploying  : Deploying container\nAnsible deploy.yml
        Injecting  : Injecting vulnerability\nAnsible inject-vulnerability.yml
        Verifying  : Verifying\nHealth + flag-protection checks

        Generating --> Deploying
        Deploying  --> Injecting
        Injecting  --> Verifying
    }

    Pipeline --> Active   : Verification passed — challenge row inserted
    Pipeline --> [*]      : Stage failed — container destroyed

    state Active {
        [*] --> Running
        Running --> Running       : User connects via SSH
        Running --> FlagSubmitted : Correct flag submitted
    }

    Active --> Completed : Flag accepted
    Active --> Expired   : TTL elapsed
    Active --> Destroyed : User clicks Destroy

    Completed --> [*]
    Expired   --> [*]
    Destroyed --> [*]
